{"article_id":"0VY4DsRbJB8vvPL4","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Donald Trump was forced to concede last week :","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"He signed a stop-gap bill","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"to temporarily fund the government for three weeks ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"ending the longest government shutdown in U.S. history .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"Unfortunately , another shutdown could be on the horizon .","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"Lawmakers are expected to hit the ground running this week","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"to ensure","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"it will not happen again .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"However , Trump will likely not concede again","depth":4},{"id":9,"text":"- he wants funding for a border wall","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"and has signaled","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"he is willing to hold out for an extended period of time","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"to get the financing .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"But","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"if it had not been for former House Speaker Paul Ryan 's seemingly weak leadership in the waning months of his congressional tenure ,","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"border wall funding may have long been secured .","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"At least that 's what Trump reportedly voiced last week during a roundtable at the White House .","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"Trump said","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"Ryan `` screwed him ''","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"by not securing funding for border security","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"- and specifically , the wall -","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"while Republicans still controlled a majority in the House ,","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"Mark Krikorian , executive director of the Center for Immigration Studies , told the Washington Post .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"[ Trump ] said","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"Ryan should have gotten him money","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"before he left","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"but he had no juice","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"and had `` gone fishing , ''","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"according to two attendees .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Ryan had warned the president against a shutdown","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"and told him","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"it would be politically disastrous ,","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"according to a person familiar with their conversations .","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"The Post 's story detailed Trump 's capitulation and the internal dialogue","depth":4},{"id":34,"text":"that happened prior","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"to Trump publicly announcing the deal","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"to re-open the government .","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"However , at the Wednesday meeting , Trump promised","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"`` there would be no caving '' to Democrats","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"-","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"the government would remain shut down","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"until border wall funding was secured .","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"`` Everybody","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"who spoke up","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"applauded him","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"for not caving ,","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"but warned him","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"that any further movement toward the Democrats ' direction would be a problem , ''","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"Krikorian said .","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"By Friday , Trump conceded ,","depth":4},{"id":50,"text":"announcing a plan","depth":5},{"id":51,"text":"to re-open the government .","depth":5},{"id":52,"text":"Many viewed the deal as a severe political blow to Trump 's agenda .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":105,"left":85,"right":104,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":85,"left":60,"right":84,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":60,"left":56,"right":59,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":56,"left":0,"right":55,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":55,"left":54,"right":3,"relation":"causal","nuc